This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2589

This color scheme was designed to look good on an OS X desktop. It has a light background, and colors that fit in well with aqua.

This color scheme is meant for use with a gui version of Vim.

Preview screenshots available at http://www.node.mu/2009/03/21/new-vim-colour-scheme-vylight/
